{
  "text": "The ISIC Challenge dataset comprised of dermoscopic skin lesion images taken by different dermatoscopes and camera devices all over the world. Hence, it is important to perform pre-processing for colour normalization and illumination with colour constancy algorithm [CITATION_1] . We processed the datasets with Shades of Gray algorithm [CITATION_2] as shown in Fig. 7 .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "88501045",
